    "This concept can be formalized through a deformation of the canonical position-momentum commutation relation.",
    "In the present analysis, we adopt a simplified isotropic realization of the EUP algebra (Hinrichsen & Kempf 1996; Mignemi 2010)",
    "where η is a small deformation parameter.",
    "This deformation implies that the effective position and momentum operator takes the form",
    "with [x i, p j ] = iℏδ ij defining the canonical structure."
